comments: Tucker (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Trent Jr. (POR) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Kanter (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the drive to the basket by Oladipo (HOU) and the contact at the rim is marginal.
Lillard (POR) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Wood (HOU) briefly places his forearm to Lillard's (POR) front and does not affect his SQBR during his drive.
Tucker (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Simons (POR) and makes marginal contact during the pick.
Kanter (POR) retreats and the marginal contact is initiated by Wall (WAS) during his driving shot attempt.
Gordon (HOU) makes contact to Lillard's (POR) body at the end of the drive but the contact is marginal.
Lillard (POR) releases from Gordon (HOU) prior to his gather on the perimeter.
Tucker (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Trent Jr. (POR) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Kanter (POR) absorbs the contact to Oladipo's (HOU) body and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Oladipo (POR) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR) as Lillard stops short in his path during the inbound.
Nwaba (HOU) makes marginal contact with Trent Jr.'s (POR) body during his driving shot attempt.
Kanter (POR) deflects the ball from Nwaba (HOU) during the rebound.
Kanter (POR) commits a take foul on Tucker (HOU).
Anthony (POR) commits a take foul on Wood (HOU).
Wood (HOU) makes marginal contact to Lillard's (POR) body after securing the loose ball.
Little (POR) commits a take foul on Gordon (HOU).
